(PNA) has agreed to have an informal meeting with Israel soon,
U.S. Middle East Peace Envoy Dennis Ross said here today.
</P>
<P>
The decision was made after Ross met with PNA President Yasser
Arafat Sunday night, a local radio report said quoting the peace
coordinator.
