when Israel started the construction of a new Jewish neighborhood
at Har Homa on the outskirts of Arab East Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
Ross briefed the Jordanian king and Majali on his efforts to
bring the stalled Israeli-Palestinian peace talks back on track,
and praised Jordan for its support for his mediation efforts, the
report said.
</P>
<P>
