<HEADLINE> Syria Sends Urgent Aid to Iranian Quake Victims </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAMASCUS, May 12 (Xinhua) -- Two Syrian aircraft flew to Iran
today carrying the first consignment of Syrian aid to the
quake-stricken victims of Iran, the Syrian news agency reported.
</P>
<P>
According to the report, the 80-tonne assistance comprises
various kinds of serums, cotton, bandages and other medicines as
well as infant milk powder.
</P>
