President Hafez al-Assad to extend every possible humanitarian
aid to the Iranian people, said Minister of Health Mohammed Iyad
Shatti in a press statement on the occasion.
</P>
<P>
The quake measuring 7.1 magnitude on the Richter scale, which
struck east Iran Saturday, has killed over 4,000 people and
wounded thousands of others in addition to the destruction of 200
villages in the area. 
