conference, which will also be attended by presidents of
Afghanistan, Azerbaijan, Iran, Kazakhstan, Kyrghizistan, Pakistan,
Uzbekistan, Tajikistan and Turkmenistan.
</P>
<P>
The ECO, originating from the former Regional Cooperation and
Development Organization, was set up by Turkey, Pakistan and Iran
in 1985. 
