<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, May 12 (Xinhua) -- Two fires have destroyed nearly 150
hectares of forest and the same area of grass and bush in Bulgaria
on Friday and Sunday.
</P>
<P>
About 150 hectares of 40- to 100-year-old coniferous trees were
destroyed near Smolian in southwestern Bulgaria on Friday.
</P>
