<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, May 12 (Xinhua) -- A former manager of Adam Opel AG, the
German subsidiary of the U.S. carmaker General Motors (GM), went
on trial today in Germany on charges of blackmail and bribery,
said German media reports.
</P>
